    "GeneratedID": null,
    "GeneratedIDReason": null,
    "Namespace": null,
    "Section": null,
    "Text": "1. On 23 October 2018, the Committee registered the communication and requested the State party to take interim measures to suspend the eviction of the author and her daughter pending the consideration of the communication or to provide them with adequate alternative housing, in genuine consultation with them.",
    "Footnotes": [],
    "Labels": [],
    "SourceFormat": "docx"
  },
  {
    "ID": "2.",
    "OriginalID": null,
    "RawID": null,
    "IdCorrection": null,
    "GeneratedID": null,
    "GeneratedIDReason": null,
    "Namespace": null,
    "Section": null,
    "Text": "2. At its meeting on 28 February 2022, the Committee, having taken note of the State party’s request for discontinuance and of the author’s withdrawal of the case on the grounds that alternative housing had been granted, decided to discontinue consideration of communication No. 67/2018, in accordance with rule 18 of its rules of procedure under the Optional Protocol.",
